Name: Team Up VR (Beta)
About the game: Team Up is a virtual reality enabled multiplayer sci-fi shooter game where 6 players are pitted against one another in a 3 vs. 3 match. Immerse yourself in the world of ultimate war between Terminators and Humans. Choose your hero from different playable characters. Fight and claim your victory in an epic VR death match. Features Dedicated Servers Bots Death match 10 Heroes with different weapons and abilities Touch-pad locomotion Runs on Vive, Oculus and WMR Different maps with different objectives (Soon) Offline Mode (Soon) Voice Chat (Soon)
